---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { links } from "../data/links";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support"
  description="Support Taj's Mod development. Learn about ways to contribute, report issues, and help the project grow."
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <section
    class="bg-gradient-to-b from-accent-600 to-accent-700 text-white pt-12 pb-16"
  >
    <div class="container-wide text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Support the Project</h1>
      <p class="text-accent-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
        Taj's Mod is free and has it's source code available on GitHub. Here's
        how you can help keep it going.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <!-- Transparency Notice -->
      <div
        class="card bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 mb-12"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">ğŸ”’</div>
          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-900 dark:text-green-100"
            >
              Full Transparency
            </h2>
            <p class="text-green-800 dark:text-green-200">
              Taj's Mod is completely free and will always remain so. There are
              no hidden paywalls, no locked features, and no "premium" tiers.
              All gameplay-affecting features are clearly labeled as opt-in.
              Your tokens and progression are never touched without explicit
              action from you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ways to Support -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Ways to Support</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">â­</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Rate on Workshop</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            A positive rating helps others discover the mod. It takes just a
            second and makes a big difference.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3628222709"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            Rate on Steam
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">ğŸ›</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Report Bugs</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            Found something broken? Report it on GitHub so it can be fixed in
            the next update.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TajemnikTV/TajsMod/issues/new"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            Report Issue
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">ğŸ’¡</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Suggest Features</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            Have an idea for a new feature? Many current features came from
            community suggestions!
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TajemnikTV/TajsMod/issues/new"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            Suggest Feature
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">ğŸ§ª</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Beta Testing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            Help test new features before they're released. Join the Discord to
            get notified about beta builds.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/enigmadev"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            Join Discord
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">ğŸ’»</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Contribute Code</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            Know GDScript? Pull requests are welcome! Check the contributing
            guidelines on GitHub.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TajemnikTV/TajsMod"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            View on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">ğŸ“£</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Spread the Word</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
            Tell other Upload Labs players about the mod. Word of mouth is the
            best advertising.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3628222709"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-secondary text-sm"
          >
            Share on Steam
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Why Support? -->
      <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-dark-800 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Why Support Matters</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Every bit of support â€” whether it's a bug report, a feature
          suggestion, or just a kind word â€” helps motivate continued
          development. This mod started as a personal project and grew into
          something the community uses and enjoys. Your feedback shapes what
          comes next.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
